WEBVTT

00:00.800 --> 00:02.366
[theme music]

00:11.133 --> 00:14.633
♪ Sometimes the world
looks perfect ♪

00:14.666 --> 00:17.166
♪ Nothin' to rearrange ♪

00:17.200 --> 00:20.233
♪ Sometimes you just
get a feelin' ♪

00:20.266 --> 00:24.600
♪ Like you need
some kinda change ♪

00:24.633 --> 00:28.200
♪ No matter what the odds
are this time ♪

00:28.233 --> 00:30.533
♪ Nothing's gonna
stand in my way ♪

00:30.566 --> 00:32.333
♪ This flame in my heart ♪

00:32.366 --> 00:33.600
♪ Like a long lost friend ♪

00:33.633 --> 00:39.266
<i>♪ Gives every dark street</i>
<i>a light at the end ♪</i>

00:39.300 --> 00:42.100
♪ Standin' tall ♪

00:42.133 --> 00:45.700
♪ On the wings
