00:45.733 --> 00:48.633
♪ Rise and fall ♪

00:48.666 --> 00:52.466
♪ On the wings
of my dreams ♪

00:52.500 --> 00:54.200
♪ Through the rain
and thunder ♪

00:54.233 --> 00:55.633
♪ The wind and haze ♪

00:55.666 --> 00:59.300
♪ I'm bound
